Monster Trio

Vinsmoke Sanji

Sanji is the Straw Hat Pirates' cook. A chivalrous gentleman, he uses his powerful legs for a unique fighting style, and his ultimate dream is to find the legendary sea known as the All Blue.

Monkey D Luffy

Luffy is the captain of the Straw Hat Pirates. A cheerful and simple-minded rubber man, he uses his stretchy body to fight, and his ultimate dream is to find the One Piece and become the Pirate King.

Roronoa Zoro

Zoro is the Straw Hat Pirates' first mate. A serious and ambitious swordsman, he uses his unique Three Sword Style, and his ultimate dream is to become the world's greatest swordsman.
